"This view showcases all the events in the database in their respective "
"stages. By default, the stages "
"are: :guilabel:`New`, :guilabel:`Booked`, :guilabel:`Announced`, :guilabel:`Ended`, "
"and :guilabel:`Cancelled`."
msgstr ""

