#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/community_rooms.rst:49
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Max capacity`: Select the maximum number of participants allowed "
"in the room."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/community_rooms.rst:50
msgid ":guilabel:`Language`: Select the language of the meeting."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/community_rooms.rst:52
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Chat Room` field is automatically populated with a generated "
"name for the *Jitsi* conference room. If desired, the user can change this "
"name by clicking the field and modifying any details on the resulting form."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/community_rooms.rst:56
msgid ""
